.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">慎防失憶</span>"},{"pid":"eb25244154e99fe12dfc632f9514630ceec314d1","tid":455404,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5d3353b130cb5051b1f37b758a4024defce53a","tid":455404,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>假設題：香港同巴基斯坦足球友誼賽，響旺角場踼，有一班持有三粒星嘅巴基斯坦人入場支持巴基斯坦，響奏中國國歌時噓國歌，呢班人係香港人，會否因國歌法而被拉？</blockquote><br />\n桂民海有瑞典護照都俾中國當中國人啦<br />\n中國想你係中國人就係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那共匪唔承認雙重國籍嘛，但佢地自己同老婆仔女都揸綠卡、澳洲、加拿大、新西蘭&hellip;&hellip;護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e56a69471bb535f3a8e97c05e084865f69322d","tid":455404,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfd49e42cbd73f75791d04b19d4a6dfa356e7d8","tid":455404,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1683c0b89e6a74eaf3074b18e67722da19e79e9","tid":455404,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c164d943d8b36e503bd2619628de18641332f1","tid":455404,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9a4249ae2f4bdfe3975a98adc8e2b0e1b66c9b","tid":455404,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.g